      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It\u2019s been pampered since day one and is in absolutely pristine, showroom-ready condition\u2014it basically still has that new car smell! It drives like a total dream and looks even better. If you\u2019re looking for a real gem that\u2019s been loved every mile of the way, this is the one for you. Drop me a message, I'd love to show it to you!",
