    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2011 Porsche 911 Carrera is a true collector\u2019s dream, preserved in showroom condition. The Guards Red paint retains its deep, glass-like luster, free of chips or swirls, and is protected by a full front-end clear bra. Inside, the Sand Beige leather remains supple and firm, smelling exactly as it did the day it left Stuttgart, with no bolster wear or creasing. Every button and switch operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is flawless, backed by a comprehensive service history and a recent major service including new Michelin Pilot Sport tires. It has been garage-kept under a soft cover in a climate-controlled environment. This is an investment-grade example for the discerning driver who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
